title: John McLaughlin - Entrevue 2009 (anglais)
description:
En marge du concert du Five Peace Band dans le cadre de la série Jazz à l'année 2009, le guitariste John McLaughlin nous livre diverses réflexions sur sa conception de la musique. [En anglais]
---
Following his concert with the Five Peace Band as part of the 2009 Jazz All Year Round series, pianist and composer John McLaughlin shares his thoughts on jazz, musicianship and his long time collaboration with pianist Chick Corea.
